WEBVTT

00:15.750 --> 00:16.510
How is he?

00:18.160 --> 00:20.070
I've used acupuncture
to regulate his blood and qi.

00:20.070 --> 00:22.260
The poison won't reach
his heart for the time being.

00:22.260 --> 00:24.290
He will wake up in a few days.

00:25.600 --> 00:26.390
But...

00:27.320 --> 00:28.120
But what?

00:30.320 --> 00:32.400
Instead of neutralizing this poison,
I can only slow the poison's progress.

00:32.400 --> 00:34.080
But I can't do that this time.

00:34.430 --> 00:36.070
If we still can't find the antidote,

00:36.070 --> 00:38.470
he has a month at best,
just 10 days at worst,

00:38.560 --> 00:39.690
and I can't save him.

02:02.140 --> 02:07.360
[REBIRTH]

02:07.850 --> 02:10.270
[Episode 25]

02:13.680 --> 02:15.630
Great Yan has endured months
of severe drought this year,

02:15.630 --> 02:17.430
leaving the autumn harvest poor.

02:17.430 --> 02:20.360
Except for the Hongchuan and Pale Tribes,
which have surpluses,

02:20.360 --> 02:24.310
other tribes' elders have written
to request emergency grain supplies.

02:24.310 --> 02:25.079
However...

02:27.590 --> 02:30.360
However, the granaries
in the Capital of Great Yan

02:30.360 --> 02:32.730
have long been used
to supply the military.

02:32.730 --> 02:34.260
What about
the elder of the Hongchuan Tribe?

02:34.260 --> 02:36.060
Elder Tubu
of the Hongchuan Tribe claimed

02:36.060 --> 02:37.840
that due to the continuous rain
these past few days,

02:37.840 --> 02:39.400
his leg ailment has flared up,

02:39.400 --> 02:40.960
so he asked for leave
to recuperate at home.

02:40.960 --> 02:43.250
Hasn't there been a severe drought
for months?

02:43.250 --> 02:43.970
Why?

02:44.550 --> 02:46.680
Did the Hongchuan Tribe pray for rain?

02:47.360 --> 02:48.430
What about Elder Pale?

02:48.430 --> 02:49.890
Did he get rheumatism too?

02:50.000 --> 02:53.460
Elder Pale went hunting in Mount Hei
the day before yesterday.

02:53.670 --> 02:56.150
It's said he broke his leg
because his horse was startled.

02:56.150 --> 02:56.910
Your Majesty,

02:56.910 --> 02:58.120
they are going too far.

02:58.120 --> 02:58.960
They are just unwilling

02:58.960 --> 03:00.870
to bring out their surplus grain
for emergencies.

03:00.870 --> 03:02.600
What kind of excuses are those?

03:04.590 --> 03:05.390
Your Majesty,

03:05.560 --> 03:07.030
we can't blame the elders.

03:07.240 --> 03:08.700
In the defeat of Great Yan,

03:08.960 --> 03:11.030
every tribe suffered heavy casualties.

03:11.030 --> 03:12.630
Except for
the relatively wealthy Hongchuan

03:12.630 --> 03:13.590
and Pale Tribes,

03:13.680 --> 03:14.360
the other tribes

03:14.360 --> 03:15.800
have almost no labor force left

03:15.800 --> 03:16.800
for farming.

03:17.360 --> 03:19.079
Elder Hongchuan and Elder Pale

03:19.079 --> 03:20.840
saw the desolation in the other tribes

03:20.840 --> 03:24.240
and were afraid, so they didn't want
to bring out their grain.

03:39.590 --> 03:41.030
Show some mercy.

03:44.660 --> 03:45.530
Don't touch me.

03:47.750 --> 03:48.960
Wake up.

03:49.680 --> 03:50.280
Father.

03:55.680 --> 03:56.960
Show some mercy.

04:03.750 --> 04:04.710
My son!

04:04.830 --> 04:05.830
-Mother!
-My son!

04:06.150 --> 04:06.710
Mother!

04:07.080 --> 04:07.680
My son!

04:07.680 --> 04:08.360
Come back.

04:08.520 --> 04:09.030
Mother!

04:11.470 --> 04:13.000
Sir, I'm sorry.

04:13.680 --> 04:16.040
My mother is sick
and doesn't recognize anyone.

04:16.040 --> 04:17.170
Please forgive her.

04:18.120 --> 04:19.800
My husband was in the army of Great Yan.

04:19.800 --> 04:21.730
He went to war and didn't come back.

04:22.000 --> 04:24.050
My mother's lost her mind over the years,

04:24.050 --> 04:25.390
and she doesn't recognize people anymore.

04:25.390 --> 04:25.920
But

04:26.310 --> 04:28.680
she recognizes the sound
of the bell on the horse's reins.

04:28.680 --> 04:30.210
Whenever soldiers pass by,

04:30.510 --> 04:31.830
she will grab them

04:32.090 --> 04:33.620
and call my husband's name.

04:34.630 --> 04:36.480
My son, you're back.

04:41.870 --> 04:42.640
My son.

04:45.750 --> 04:46.950
Sir, please spare us!

04:47.920 --> 04:49.120
Sir, please spare us!

04:49.190 --> 04:50.040
My son.

04:50.870 --> 04:52.480
My son, you're back.

04:53.070 --> 04:54.750
My son, you're back.

04:58.800 --> 04:59.750
My son.

05:05.160 --> 05:08.070
My son, you're back.

05:12.920 --> 05:14.480
My son gave me money.

05:15.310 --> 05:17.360
My son gave me money.

05:18.720 --> 05:19.600
Thank you, Sir.

05:19.780 --> 05:21.910
-My son gave me money.
-Thank you, Sir.

05:33.120 --> 05:33.800
In the past,

05:34.170 --> 05:38.920
[Capital of Great Yan]

05:34.830 --> 05:36.560
my father and the Emperor of Great Yong

05:36.560 --> 05:39.020
conquered most of the northeastern plains.

05:40.270 --> 05:42.390
The Emperor of Great Yong
designated the area north of Yanming Pass

05:42.390 --> 05:43.360
as Great Yan

05:43.920 --> 05:45.250
and gave it to my father.

05:46.040 --> 05:46.630
He said

05:48.310 --> 05:50.570
if the territory of Great Yong was a wolf,

05:51.950 --> 05:52.950
then Great Yan

05:54.040 --> 05:55.440
would be the wolf's head.

05:57.120 --> 05:58.830
As long as Great Yan was guarded,

05:58.830 --> 06:01.760
two-thirds of Great Yong's borders
would be secure.

06:02.070 --> 06:03.000
To guard

06:03.000 --> 06:04.860
these two-thirds of the borders,

06:07.270 --> 06:08.730
my father built this city.

06:09.270 --> 06:11.120
The walls of the Capital of Great Yan

06:11.120 --> 06:12.920
remain impregnable to this day.

06:13.240 --> 06:15.310
It shows the late king's foresight.

06:26.070 --> 06:28.470
But now, only the city walls
remain strong.

06:29.800 --> 06:30.930
The entire Great Yan

06:31.950 --> 06:33.950
is already stretched to its limits.

06:38.900 --> 06:39.670
Cheng Yuan,

06:40.120 --> 06:41.720
I failed to defend Great Yan

06:42.040 --> 06:44.000
or my father's legacy.

06:48.190 --> 06:48.990
Your Majesty.

06:49.630 --> 06:50.720
Without you,

06:52.070 --> 06:53.670
Great Yan would be long gone.

06:53.830 --> 06:54.920
Great Yong is a wolf,

06:54.920 --> 06:56.190
and Biantang is the vast forest

06:56.190 --> 06:57.450
surrounding the wolf.

06:57.600 --> 06:59.390
We lost the battle at Longyin Pass.

06:59.390 --> 07:00.160
If we had won,

07:00.870 --> 07:02.510
the wolf would've been attacked
from both sides

07:02.510 --> 07:04.310
and become our prey.

07:04.720 --> 07:06.560
You did it not just for Queen Chu

07:06.560 --> 07:07.750
but for Great Yan.

07:09.270 --> 07:11.000
Others may not understand you,

07:12.000 --> 07:12.870
but I do.

07:28.040 --> 07:29.750
In the battle against Biantang,

07:29.750 --> 07:31.880
Your Majesty, you only lost Queen Chu,

07:32.110 --> 07:34.680
but Great Yan and I are still here.

07:35.159 --> 07:37.950
Great Yan, you, and I are one.

07:39.159 --> 07:40.820
Life or death, glory or shame,

07:40.830 --> 07:41.870
in heaven or hell,

07:42.830 --> 07:43.950
always and forever,

07:43.950 --> 07:44.480
I

07:45.870 --> 07:47.530
stand with you, Your Majesty.

08:22.320 --> 08:26.300
♪ The sky is so vast ♪

08:26.320 --> 08:28.810
♪ The dark clouds are gray ♪

08:31.200 --> 08:34.960
♪ The rain is falling ♪

08:34.980 --> 08:38.340
♪ The eagle is flying ♪

08:40.030 --> 08:43.820
♪ In the vast wilderness ♪

08:43.840 --> 08:47.310
♪ The wind blows ♪

08:49.340 --> 08:52.410
♪ I'm fearless of death ♪

08:52.640 --> 08:56.170
♪ And I'll never have regrets ♪

08:58.500 --> 09:06.010
♪ The lonely black eagle ♪

09:07.500 --> 09:10.830
♪ Is flying against the light ♪

09:11.640 --> 09:14.840
♪ Where is my hometown? ♪

09:15.380 --> 09:24.340
♪ In the vast world ♪

09:24.360 --> 09:27.770
♪ I have no origin ♪

09:28.430 --> 09:32.020
♪ And no destination ♪

09:32.590 --> 09:40.640
♪ A pair of stubborn wings ♪

09:40.870 --> 09:49.140
♪ Is born to fly ♪

10:05.030 --> 10:05.750
Don't look.

10:06.630 --> 10:07.390
Go home.

10:08.270 --> 10:09.360
Go, go.

10:12.510 --> 10:13.840
Here is your tea.

10:13.840 --> 10:14.900
Sorry for the wait.

10:15.600 --> 10:16.230
Sir.

10:17.270 --> 10:18.870
Who are those corpses

10:19.200 --> 10:21.200
hanging on the city gate over there?

10:21.200 --> 10:23.270
They were slaves
from King Ximeng's Palace,

10:23.270 --> 10:25.550
executed by King Ximeng
for making mistakes.

10:25.550 --> 10:26.950
I've been here for 3 days.

10:27.150 --> 10:28.390
Every day, different people

10:28.390 --> 10:29.510
would be hung up here.

10:29.510 --> 10:32.130
How many people
does King Ximeng kill a day?

10:32.600 --> 10:34.130
Keep your voice down, Miss.

10:34.560 --> 10:36.550
I can see you two are not from Ximeng.

10:36.550 --> 10:38.960
It's too conspicuous
to say such things on the street.

10:38.960 --> 10:40.820
If those Ximeng soldiers hear it,

10:40.840 --> 10:42.000
not to mention you two,

10:42.000 --> 10:43.200
even I won't survive.

10:53.390 --> 10:54.320
Are these slaves

10:54.550 --> 10:56.350
newly presented to King Ximeng?

10:56.550 --> 10:57.150
Yes.

10:57.910 --> 10:59.840
Go up the mountain out of this gate,

10:59.840 --> 11:01.440
and you'll reach the palace.

11:02.460 --> 11:03.500
Enjoy your tea.

11:03.520 --> 11:05.120
I'll see to the other guests.

11:11.080 --> 11:11.750
Yue Shiyi?

11:16.270 --> 11:16.960
Yue Shiyi.

11:18.380 --> 11:19.310
Why are you here?

11:19.470 --> 11:21.480
I went with the Young Master
to rescue the Queen of Lingyue.

11:21.480 --> 11:22.550
At the agreed place,

11:22.550 --> 11:23.790
he didn't show up.

11:24.320 --> 11:26.510
So I returned to the city
to find some clues

11:26.510 --> 11:27.510
and happened to meet you.

11:27.510 --> 11:29.200
His poison flared up again.

11:29.200 --> 11:31.000
He's recuperating
at the Queen of Lingyue's place.

11:31.000 --> 11:32.400
He is in no danger for now.

11:34.240 --> 11:34.870
Hurry up.

11:36.880 --> 11:39.340
These have to be sent
into the inner palace tonight.

11:39.340 --> 11:40.260
We can't delay.

11:40.790 --> 11:41.440
Hurry up.

11:41.780 --> 11:43.110
Why are these carriages

11:43.540 --> 11:45.540
different from the ones we just saw?

11:45.630 --> 11:47.630
I asked around among the commoners.

11:47.840 --> 11:49.550
Under these black cloths

11:49.720 --> 11:51.630
are personal female slaves
sent into the palace.

11:51.630 --> 11:53.080
Because of their special status,
they can't be seen,

11:53.080 --> 11:55.140
so they are covered with black cloth.

11:56.280 --> 11:57.720
I went to scout during the day.

11:57.720 --> 11:59.200
King Ximeng's Palace
is built against the mountain,

11:59.200 --> 12:00.440
supported by huge rocks.

12:00.440 --> 12:02.030
There is an inner palace
inside the royal palace.

12:02.030 --> 12:04.160
The outer palace
is a long stone-stepped corridor.

12:04.160 --> 12:04.910
The inner palace

12:04.910 --> 12:06.620
is where King Ximeng lives.

12:08.080 --> 12:10.000
Those carriages covered with black cloth

12:10.000 --> 12:11.960
should be the ones
sent to serve in the inner palace.

12:11.960 --> 12:12.630
I suppose so.

12:12.630 --> 12:13.510
If only those carriages

12:13.510 --> 12:15.040
can enter the inner palace,

12:15.670 --> 12:16.910
let me go.

12:17.510 --> 12:19.550
I used to be a slave in Zhenhuangcheng.

12:19.550 --> 12:20.750
I know better than you

12:20.770 --> 12:22.170
how not to be exposed.

12:22.390 --> 12:22.910
My Lady,

12:23.230 --> 12:25.080
you must remember this map clearly.

12:25.080 --> 12:26.320
There are many mountain paths
in the outer palace

12:26.320 --> 12:27.200
to escape from.

12:27.290 --> 12:28.410
But our priority

12:28.440 --> 12:30.370
is to leave the inner palace first.

12:30.390 --> 12:32.360
We may not be able
to enter Ximeng's inner palace,

12:32.360 --> 12:33.550
so you must rely on yourself

12:33.550 --> 12:34.700
to remember the way to escape.

12:34.700 --> 12:36.360
The inner palace is enclosed
by 8 layers of octagonal palace walls.

12:36.360 --> 12:38.150
Every road leads to somewhere,
yet also nowhere.

12:38.150 --> 12:39.110
The terrain is complex.

12:39.110 --> 12:41.010
You must remember
every turning point clearly.

12:41.010 --> 12:42.230
Once you take the wrong fork,

12:42.230 --> 12:44.000
it will be extremely difficult to get out.

12:44.000 --> 12:45.240
After you enter Ximeng's inner palace

12:45.240 --> 12:46.360
and get the antidote,

12:46.360 --> 12:48.550
you can exit through the south corner gate
via the outer palace's mountain path.

12:48.550 --> 12:50.550
Minglu and I will wait for you there.

13:04.240 --> 13:05.270
I will go with you.

13:05.940 --> 13:07.600
I just went to check on the Young Master.

13:07.600 --> 13:08.790
He's still in a coma.

13:09.030 --> 13:10.890
I can't help much by staying here.

13:14.120 --> 13:15.520
I can stay here by myself.

13:18.000 --> 13:19.060
It's getting late.

13:19.360 --> 13:20.360
Let's go.

14:00.030 --> 14:01.090
Hurry up, hurry up!

14:01.190 --> 14:02.240
Before the third watch,

14:02.240 --> 14:03.750
be sure to send them
into the inner palace!

14:03.750 --> 14:04.550
Hurry up, hurry up!

14:04.550 --> 14:05.080
Get down!

14:06.630 --> 14:07.440
Hurry up!

15:15.530 --> 15:16.600
You wait here.

15:17.190 --> 15:18.280
I'll be right back.

15:40.830 --> 15:41.680
This incense

15:42.030 --> 15:43.480
smells so good.

15:44.800 --> 15:46.650
Maybe it's to relax us.

15:50.510 --> 15:51.560
My eyes!

15:52.270 --> 15:53.820
I can't see anything!

15:53.840 --> 15:54.940
There's something wrong with this incense!

15:54.940 --> 15:56.340
Close your eyes quickly!

15:59.880 --> 16:00.830
My eyes!

16:01.360 --> 16:02.960
I can't see anything!

16:02.960 --> 16:04.440
I can't see!

16:04.460 --> 16:05.440
My eyes!

16:05.440 --> 16:07.500
Quickly cover your eyes with a cloth!

16:33.840 --> 16:34.960
Congratulations.

16:35.280 --> 16:37.540
You will all become King Ximeng's women.

16:38.200 --> 16:40.870
From now on, you'll live in luxury.

16:40.870 --> 16:42.840
You won't need your eyes anymore.

17:04.160 --> 17:05.880
The inner palace is enclosed
by 8 layers of octagonal palace walls.

17:05.880 --> 17:07.010
The terrain is complex.

17:07.010 --> 17:09.030
You must remember
every turning point clearly.

17:09.030 --> 17:10.130
Once you take the wrong fork,

17:10.130 --> 17:12.460
it will be extremely difficult to get out.

17:14.920 --> 17:17.020
The female slaves
selected to enter the inner palace

17:17.020 --> 17:19.440
will be branded with
a plum blossom mark on their arms.

17:19.440 --> 17:20.440
With this mark,

17:20.869 --> 17:22.270
they will let you in.

17:39.590 --> 17:40.680
Keep going.

17:41.160 --> 17:42.160
Move forward.

17:43.180 --> 17:43.770
Hurry up.

18:18.640 --> 18:20.030
Who are you?

18:20.640 --> 18:21.480
Your Majesty.

18:22.280 --> 18:24.810
I am a refugee fleeing from Great Yan.

18:25.350 --> 18:26.810
My parents have both died.

18:27.110 --> 18:29.640
I had to wander to Ximeng to survive.

18:30.200 --> 18:31.350
A refugee.

18:32.200 --> 18:35.400
Then why are there blade scars
on your back?

18:36.070 --> 18:38.660
I encountered robbers on the way.

18:39.160 --> 18:40.490
I was seriously injured

18:40.750 --> 18:42.590
and tried my best to escape here,

18:42.960 --> 18:44.270
just to survive.

18:44.560 --> 18:46.800
I came to serve you voluntarily.

18:47.270 --> 18:49.750
I'm willing to serve you.

18:50.510 --> 18:53.240
As long as I can live and get to eat,

18:54.240 --> 18:56.510
I'll always stay by your side.

19:03.720 --> 19:04.920
Come here.

20:03.880 --> 20:05.280
You held weapons before?

20:09.270 --> 20:10.240
Who are you?

20:16.380 --> 20:18.510
Where is the antidote to Blood on Snow?

20:21.840 --> 20:23.350
Tell me, or I will kill you.

20:50.070 --> 20:52.270
You are the real King Ximeng.

20:58.310 --> 20:58.840
Hurry!

20:59.160 --> 21:00.350
Oh no. They are Ximeng soldiers.

21:00.350 --> 21:00.880
Go!

21:02.740 --> 21:03.300
This way!

21:03.640 --> 21:04.840
This way! Chase them!

21:07.510 --> 21:08.160
Hurry!

21:09.310 --> 21:10.400
Stop! Chase them!

21:10.590 --> 21:11.310
Stop!

21:13.340 --> 21:14.680
-We are exposed! Hurry!
-Don't run!

21:14.680 --> 21:16.030
-This way!
-Run! Run!

21:16.200 --> 21:16.830
Stop!

21:19.510 --> 21:20.160
Don't run!

21:36.110 --> 21:37.790
I know who you are.

21:38.310 --> 21:39.400
Seven years ago,

21:39.720 --> 21:41.380
an escaped slave of Great Yong

21:41.400 --> 21:44.640
raised an army in Zhenhuangcheng
with the Heir Apparent of Great Yan,

21:44.640 --> 21:47.640
catching the late emperor of Great Yong
off guard.

21:48.550 --> 21:50.550
I respect you for your courage.

21:51.240 --> 21:54.200
When Zhuge Yue's body
is brought back later,

21:54.440 --> 21:56.880
I will let you die together.

22:14.850 --> 22:16.160
You betrayed us.

22:57.840 --> 22:59.590
What are you going to do to Zhuge Yue?

22:59.590 --> 23:01.310
To save you, Zhuge Yue

23:01.400 --> 23:04.190
traded his life with me.

23:04.210 --> 23:06.010
He broke his promise first

23:06.040 --> 23:07.520
and refused to be my slave.

23:07.720 --> 23:09.590
Even if I don't kill him,

23:10.020 --> 23:12.260
he won't live much longer.

23:15.590 --> 23:16.860
I don't want to kill you.

23:16.860 --> 23:17.990
Don't force my hand.

23:21.070 --> 23:23.400
The Emperor of Great Yong is incompetent.

23:23.440 --> 23:25.280
A mere female slave

23:25.400 --> 23:28.110
has turned Great Yong
and Great Yan upside down.

23:29.200 --> 23:32.240
I heard you also abolished slavery
in Biantang.

23:33.400 --> 23:34.590
Let me tell you,

23:34.590 --> 23:36.640
slaves are the most lowly
and inferior animals.

23:36.640 --> 23:38.640
They barely have enough to eat or wear

23:38.640 --> 23:40.400
and are barely considered human!

23:40.400 --> 23:42.530
And you still vainly hope to save them?

23:43.510 --> 23:44.240
Fine.

23:44.400 --> 23:46.510
Then I will let you know

23:46.750 --> 23:48.680
what a slave really is.

23:50.880 --> 23:52.750
Throw her into the slave pen.

23:52.960 --> 23:54.840
Let her and her companions

23:55.830 --> 23:57.880
get along well.

24:35.200 --> 24:35.750
Xing.

24:38.240 --> 24:39.160
Xiao Ran.

24:40.620 --> 24:41.420
Where is Xing?

24:42.070 --> 24:43.480
Is Xing here too?

24:43.790 --> 24:45.120
Lie down and don't move.

24:46.750 --> 24:48.240
I am applying acupuncture needles.

24:48.240 --> 24:50.530
These needles can temporarily
suppress the heat poison in your body,

24:50.530 --> 24:53.660
so you can live a few more days
until you get the antidote.

25:10.550 --> 25:11.280
Xing.

25:11.310 --> 25:12.790
I will go outside to brew your medicine.

25:12.790 --> 25:14.720
Lie quietly and don't move around.

25:18.070 --> 25:19.670
There is some noise outside.

25:55.720 --> 25:57.720
General Chu has gone to
King Ximeng's Palace for your antidote.

25:57.720 --> 25:59.050
I fear she's in trouble.

26:02.480 --> 26:03.610
No one is in the room!

26:03.960 --> 26:05.220
They should be nearby.

26:05.840 --> 26:06.770
Keep searching!

26:19.590 --> 26:20.880
The sheep has fallen into the trap.

26:20.880 --> 26:22.340
Why haven't you acted yet?

26:22.680 --> 26:23.830
Is your aim true?

26:24.920 --> 26:26.590
That's the castor powder
I spent a long time developing.

26:26.590 --> 26:27.450
Don't waste it.

26:35.990 --> 26:36.680
There's no one here.

26:36.680 --> 26:38.410
-No one's here.
-No one's here.

28:00.160 --> 28:00.960
Your Majesty,

28:01.110 --> 28:02.480
I've failed to kill Zhuge Yue.

28:02.480 --> 28:03.480
My sins are grave.

28:03.680 --> 28:05.480
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

28:09.110 --> 28:11.480
As long as you kill Zhuge Yue,

28:11.590 --> 28:14.400
I'll give you the antidote
to Blood on Snow.

28:24.880 --> 28:25.680
Your Majesty.

28:26.880 --> 28:28.790
I can give you the antidote,

28:28.790 --> 28:31.200
but you must take
your crazy man and leave,

28:31.200 --> 28:32.430
the further the better.

28:32.430 --> 28:35.030
From now on, there will be no Lingyue Clan
in Ximeng.

28:35.030 --> 28:37.250
As long as they obediently
become Ximeng people

28:37.250 --> 28:38.570
and submit to me,

28:38.990 --> 28:41.710
I will spare their lives.

28:42.350 --> 28:43.750
Thank you, Your Majesty.

28:46.440 --> 28:47.110
By the way,

28:48.400 --> 28:51.480
I have a gift for you.

28:51.750 --> 28:52.830
Follow me.

29:01.080 --> 29:02.210
Alright.

29:14.920 --> 29:15.550
Baze!

29:16.020 --> 29:19.460
There's one thing I've never figured out.

29:20.240 --> 29:22.160
You said earlier that in Biantang,

29:22.160 --> 29:24.480
you accidentally let Zhuge Yue escape,

29:24.640 --> 29:27.200
and that you lied out of fear of me.

29:27.550 --> 29:29.680
Since he knew you wanted to kill him,

29:29.680 --> 29:31.310
why would he travel thousands of miles

29:31.310 --> 29:33.270
from Biantang to save you?

29:33.880 --> 29:36.680
So I summoned Baze to ask.

29:37.030 --> 29:38.350
I didn't expect him

29:38.350 --> 29:40.400
to be so loyal to you.

29:40.480 --> 29:42.350
No matter how I tortured him,

29:42.350 --> 29:44.790
he insisted that he released Zhuge Yue

29:44.790 --> 29:46.800
and privately went to send him a message,

29:46.800 --> 29:48.150
asking him to come and save you,

29:48.150 --> 29:50.450
while you knew nothing about it.

29:54.080 --> 29:55.990
He's such a loyal subordinate.

29:56.270 --> 29:58.790
I think you must like him very much,

29:58.900 --> 30:01.820
so I spared his life,

30:02.590 --> 30:04.720
as a reward for you.

30:05.550 --> 30:06.830
Remember,

30:07.240 --> 30:09.170
there won't be him alone.

30:09.350 --> 30:10.960
If it happens again,

30:11.160 --> 30:12.400
you will receive

30:12.980 --> 30:15.270
more rewards.

30:28.420 --> 30:29.420
Whoever kills her

30:30.070 --> 30:32.640
can have 2 steamed buns tonight.

31:14.460 --> 31:16.550
-Don't run!
-Stop!

31:19.800 --> 31:20.280
Go.

31:27.700 --> 31:28.600
Report!

31:32.380 --> 31:33.180
Your Majesty.

31:33.220 --> 31:36.400
General Meng En has brought back
Zhuge Yue from Great Yong.

31:36.400 --> 31:37.400
You mean

31:38.800 --> 31:41.210
he has brought Zhuge Yue back alive?

31:41.240 --> 31:41.830
Exactly.

31:42.820 --> 31:44.240
Go wait in the main hall.

31:44.830 --> 31:46.400
Summon the Queen of Lingyue.

31:46.400 --> 31:46.960
Yes.

31:53.390 --> 31:54.500
Eat.

32:09.190 --> 32:10.650
Greetings, Your Majesty.

32:10.670 --> 32:12.230
Zhuge Yue.

32:13.350 --> 32:15.070
Didn't I tell you to kill him?

32:15.090 --> 32:16.240
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

32:16.240 --> 32:17.440
I couldn't kill him.

32:26.160 --> 32:27.720
You've been poisoned
by my castor powder.

32:27.720 --> 32:29.200
You'll soon bleed
from your 7 orifices and die.

32:29.200 --> 32:31.200
Don't move if you want the antidote.

32:32.070 --> 32:33.070
Where is Chu Qiao?

32:46.500 --> 32:47.870
Someone, kill him!

32:48.000 --> 32:49.640
Quick, gouge out his eyes!

32:53.960 --> 32:55.830
Stop hiding your handsome face,

32:56.680 --> 32:58.070
Su Gulin.

33:01.070 --> 33:02.000
What did you say?

33:04.310 --> 33:05.370
It's you, isn't it,

33:06.480 --> 33:07.720
Su Gulin?

33:08.310 --> 33:09.110
Shut up!

33:09.750 --> 33:11.110
When I was in Great Yong,

33:11.350 --> 33:12.680
I heard a story.

33:13.680 --> 33:14.720
Thirty years ago,

33:15.310 --> 33:16.840
there was a slave in Ximeng,

33:17.070 --> 33:17.880
named

33:18.000 --> 33:19.510
Su Gulin.

33:20.270 --> 33:22.030
He united with some other slaves

33:22.030 --> 33:24.880
to resist the oppression
of the slave owners in Ximeng,

33:24.880 --> 33:27.400
but was betrayed by his fellow slaves.

33:28.030 --> 33:29.030
The slave owners in Ximeng

33:29.030 --> 33:31.400
gave him the cruelest punishment
of branding his face,

33:31.400 --> 33:34.070
branding the word "slave" on his face.

33:34.880 --> 33:36.240
Everyone thought

33:36.920 --> 33:39.650
that Su Gulin
died from the branding punishment,

33:40.240 --> 33:42.830
but no one knew how he managed to survive.

33:43.350 --> 33:45.080
Later, he returned to this land

33:45.270 --> 33:46.870
and punished evil with evil,

33:47.000 --> 33:50.000
and instead became
the biggest slave owner in Ximeng,

33:50.790 --> 33:52.310
Su Gulin.

33:58.640 --> 33:59.550
You are...

34:01.390 --> 34:02.650
from the Zhuge family.

34:03.640 --> 34:04.960
The Zhuge family

34:04.960 --> 34:07.310
is the biggest slave owner

34:07.310 --> 34:09.280
that keeps slaves
for the Emperor of Great Yong.

34:09.280 --> 34:11.590
I think you must know better than I do

34:11.960 --> 34:13.280
that all these slaves

34:13.480 --> 34:15.280
are stupid and despicable.

34:15.550 --> 34:17.080
You should stand by my side.

34:17.100 --> 34:19.159
Why do you want to save a female slave?

34:19.179 --> 34:20.389
I'll ask you again,

34:21.710 --> 34:23.630
where exactly is Chu Qiao?

34:25.480 --> 34:26.480
You are late.

34:27.550 --> 34:29.150
She has been

34:30.429 --> 34:31.030
torn apart

34:31.840 --> 34:33.040
and eaten by her kind.

34:36.810 --> 34:38.639
Kill him! Don't mind me!

34:39.290 --> 34:41.480
No one will leave here alive tonight!

34:42.120 --> 34:43.449
I don't want to hurt you.

34:45.469 --> 34:46.840
I have no choice.

34:54.840 --> 34:55.400
You...

34:57.030 --> 34:59.490
You and your clan
don't want to live anymore?

35:00.670 --> 35:03.360
I want to kill you

35:03.920 --> 35:05.480
just so my clan can live on.

35:12.690 --> 35:14.480
Baze is already dead.

35:16.190 --> 35:16.800
Baze,

35:18.320 --> 35:19.360
I'm sorry.

35:20.360 --> 35:22.070
I won't let you die in vain.

35:31.950 --> 35:34.010
I won't be threatened by you anymore.

35:34.320 --> 35:35.150
All this

35:37.230 --> 35:38.710
is over!

35:44.880 --> 35:45.920
Kill me,

35:46.760 --> 35:49.620
and you'll never get
the antidote for Blood on Snow.

35:49.630 --> 35:51.230
The King of Lingyue will die.

35:52.530 --> 35:54.010
Zhuge Yue will also die.

36:01.140 --> 36:02.140
You will die too!

36:27.360 --> 36:28.110
How are you?

36:36.690 --> 36:37.560
Zhuge Yue,

36:40.090 --> 36:41.650
I-I don't owe you anymore.

36:42.500 --> 36:43.100
Lingyue.

36:45.110 --> 36:45.920
Chu Qiao...

36:47.190 --> 36:47.920
is...

36:49.240 --> 36:50.630
in the slave pen.

36:50.660 --> 36:51.910
Go save her quickly.

36:53.840 --> 36:55.550
I don't want to owe her either.

37:10.840 --> 37:11.840
I'll leave my clan

37:13.480 --> 37:14.880
to you to protect.

37:16.630 --> 37:17.510
I promise you.

37:19.170 --> 37:20.170
Zhuge Yue,

37:22.770 --> 37:24.730
can you hug me?

39:17.880 --> 39:18.710
You will all

39:20.710 --> 39:23.360
be buried with me.

40:34.010 --> 40:35.840
Everyone retreat outside the inner palace!

40:35.840 --> 40:36.900
Kill trespassers!

40:37.590 --> 40:38.070
Xing.

40:38.760 --> 40:39.960
I'm afraid this time,

40:40.070 --> 40:42.130
life and death will truly do us apart.

40:42.440 --> 40:43.040
Huan Huan.

40:43.670 --> 40:45.000
I've lost Great Yan.

40:45.490 --> 40:46.950
Can you help me get it back?

40:47.920 --> 40:49.480
The fastest way to cool him down

40:49.480 --> 40:51.760
is to immerse his whole body in ice water.

40:52.000 --> 40:53.510
You've always been protecting me.

40:53.510 --> 40:54.190
Now,

40:54.840 --> 40:56.000
it's my turn to protect you.
